The paper deals with robotic manipulation, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The use of a POMDP model for planning involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of particle filtering, which is a machine learning technique (cs.LG). The manipulation of objects involves visual observations, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper deals with the adaptation of the system dynamics model, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
